OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777021560
OL,3,CPrince Harry urges world not to lose
OL,4,Csight of Ukraine as he makes surprise
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FHarry will make a speech at the
OL,8,Fconference and tell them that the
OL,9,Fbattle here is more than a simple
OL,10,Ffight about territory.
OL,12,FHe will draw on his own military
OL,13,Fexperience and his connections with
OL,14,Fcompetitors from the Invictus Games,
OL,15,Fwhich he founded, to warn that the
OL,16,Fimpact of the war in Ukraine will last
OL,17,F"for years to come".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
