PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777021560
OL,3,CPrince Harry urges world not to lose
OL,4,Csight of Ukraine as he makes surprise
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FThe Duke will also call the abduction
OL,8,Fof Ukrainian children by Russian
OL,9,Fforces a "systematic and intentional"
OL,10,Fact which will have consequences at
OL,11,Fthe International Criminal Court.
OL,13,FThe Duke of Sussex greeted Ukrainian
OL,14,Fofficials as he arrived in Kyiv
OL,15,FThursday morning
OL,17,FHis visit to Ukraine comes at a time
OL,18,Fwhen the world's attention has been on
OL,19,Fthe Middle East, and yet Ukraine's war
OL,20,Fwith Russia is now more than four
OL,21,Fyears old.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
