PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777021560
OL,3,CPrince Harry urges world not to lose
OL,4,Csight of Ukraine as he makes surprise
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FHe will tell delegates in Kyiv on
OL,8,FThursday that the world must not
OL,9,Fbecome "numb" to this, or any other
OL,10,Fconflict.
OL,12,F"This is a war about values, not just
OL,13,Fterritory", Harry will say in his
OL,14,Fspeech.
OL,16,FThe Duke arrives in Ukraine just days
OL,17,Fafter finishing a tour of Australia
OL,18,Fwith his wife, Meghan.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@MO]tD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
