OL,3,CPrince Harry urges world not to lose
OL,4,Csight of Ukraine as he makes surprise
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FHe will support his Invictus Games
OL,8,FFoundation in Ukraine, where the
OL,9,Fnumber of severely wounded military
OL,10,Fpersonnel is growing at an alarming
OL,11,Frate.
OL,13,FHe will also see the dangerous work
OL,14,Fbeing carried out by The Halo Trust,
OL,15,Fthe de-mining charity which his mother
OL,16,FPrincess Diana famously supported in
OL,17,FAngola in 1997.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
