PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777021560
OL,3,CPrince Harry urges world not to lose
OL,4,Csight of Ukraine as he makes surprise
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FCivilians are still being injured and
OL,8,Fkilled by landmines and other Russian
OL,9,Fordnance which has been left in areas
OL,10,Fwhere fighting previously took place.
OL,12,FThe Halo Trust employs 1,300 people in
OL,13,Fde-mining work in Ukraine - its
OL,14,Flargest operation anywhere in the
OL,15,Fworld.
OL,17,FHarry said: "I'm looking forward to
OL,18,Fseeing friends and re-connecting with
OL,19,Fthe Invictus community again and
OL,20,Fstanding alongside those helping
OL,21,FUkraine win this fight."
